properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 13 at 12:53PM MST until February 14 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Cheyenne WY
properties.description:
...Travel Impacts Expected from Gusty Winds and Blowing Snow ...

* WHAT...Blowing snow.

* WHERE...Portions of Converse County, northern Carbon County,
and northwestern Albany County.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 8 PM MST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Blowing snow will
significantly reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 8 PM MST FRIDAY
